b. All skins come with a preview image similar to WordPress themes. You can also create custom skins: simply drop in a folder with the style.css and a screenshot and your skin will be available.</p>\";s:9:\"css_image\";s:12:\"feature-item\";}}i:2;a:2:{s:8:\"mod_name\";s:5:\"image\";s:12:\"mod_settings\";a:8:{s:11:\"style_image\";s:11:\"image-right\";s:9:\"url_image\";s:77:\"http://themify.me/demo/themes/builder/files/2013/06/feature-import-export.png\";s:16:\"appearance_image\";s:7:\"rounded\";s:11:\"width_image\";s:3:\"415\";s:12:\"height_image\";s:3:\"213\";s:11:\"title_image\";s:15:\"Import & Export\";s:13:\"caption_image\";s:295:\"<h4>Importing & Exporting has never been this easy, seriously.</h4>\n<p>Everything\'s been taken care of. With our data structure in place you can make fast & clean backups of your settings easily. Export will generate a downloadable file of all your settings which you can import at any time.</p>\";s:9:\"css_image\";s:12:\"feature-item\";}}}}}}i:2;a:2:{s:9:\"row_order\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"cols\";a:4:{i:0;a:2:{s:10:\"grid_class\";s:12:\"col4-1 first\";s:7:\"modules\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:8:\"mod_name\";s:5:\"image\";s:12:\"mod_settings\";a:7:{s:11:\"style_image\";s:9:\"image-top\";s:9:\"url_image\";s:76:\"http://themify.me/demo/themes/builder/files/2013/06/feature-easy-styling.jpg\";s:16:\"appearance_image\";s:7:\"rounded\";s:11:\"width_image\";s:3:\"222\";s:12:\"height_image\";s:3:\"140\";s:11:\"title_image\";s:13:\"Styling Panel\";s:13:\"caption_image\";s:57:\"Just click & select, and we\'ll do the CSS coding for you.\";}}}}i:1;a:2:{s:10:\"grid_class\";s:6:\"col4-1\";s:7:\"modules\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:8:\"mod_name\";s:5:\"image\";s:12:\"mod_settings\";a:7:{s:11:\"style_image\";s:9:\"image-top\";s:9:\"url_image\";s:76:\"http://themify.me/demo/themes/builder/files/2013/06/feature-color-picker.jpg\";s:16:\"appearance_image\";s:7:\"rounded\";s:11:\"width_image\";s:3:\"222\";s:12:\"height_image\";s:3:\"140\";s:11:\"title_image\";s:12:\"Color Picker\"